rows.label: tlk45710153_05_msg0001
rows.name:
Who could have predicted the world
would come to this?

rows.label: tlk45710153_05_msg0002
rows.name:
But it's at times like this that we all
need to help each other out more
than ever. That's why I came here.

rows.label: tlk45710153_05_msg0003
rows.name:
For some reason even the
Imperial Army are willing to
listen to what I have to say.

rows.label: tlk45710153_05_msg0004
rows.name: I'm glad I can be of help to everyone.

rows.label: tlk45710153_05_msg0005
rows.name:
We'll be all right here, I'll make
sure of it. So you can focus on
saving Alst, eh?
